{
  "stem": "17374.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We stay in Paris.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is My husband was earning very good money in Paris, and he was playing in many places-- [INAUDIBLE], or [INAUDIBLE], other places.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was earning good money, and he buying me things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then in Chamonix was casino event, but I never went down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not a few months, and I want to go to Paris too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my husband wants to go to America, because his brother were in America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My sister was in Paris.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But maybe he loves me so much, I don't know, that we went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went to Paris after a few months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My sisters sent me a letter with a photo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the photo was taken in [INAUDIBLE], somewhere, where the palms are.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I seen that, that was like a dream for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a beach, and sand, and sea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "First time I see sea, in my life, when we went to [INAUDIBLE] Australia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went by train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From-- from Paris to Australia, on was ship.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But first, we went by train to [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Genoa. ?] And then we took a ship, and takes us six weeks, I believe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sirenia ?] was the name of the ship.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when-- it was a nice ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was never seasick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some other people were, but-- and my husband was playing on the ship again, and makes everybody happy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's a few people here who come with us, two or three, on the same ship.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When did we--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Williams-- Williamsport, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Melbourne, yes, Melbourne, yes-- Henry was waiting for us-- my sister, and my brother-in-law, and some other family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't have car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but she got, already, house, my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
